	(112, 0, 53, 'Publication of style guide', 'publication-of-style-guide', '<p>The en-GB style guide has now been published and can be found at <a href="http://developer.joomla.org">http://developer.joomla.org</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Pull Requests etc since the last report</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/7523">standardise on folder&nbsp;</a>- Merged PR</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/7469">Simplify text and Elminitate Redundancy for JLIB_RULES_SETTING_NOTES</a>&nbsp;- Merged PR</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://issues.joomla.org/tracker/joomla-cms/7637">Batch Processing Instructions </a>- Merged PR</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://issues.joomla.org/tracker/joomla-cms/7650">Toggle All Selection - menu assignment </a>- Merged PR</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://issues.joomla.org/tracker/joomla-cms/6555">Rename Custom Html module to custom</a> - Pending PR</p>\r\n<p><a href="https://github.com/joomla/user-interface-text/issues/11">Viewlevel Access - Consistency Check</a>&nbsp;- In Progress</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 0, 0, 448, '2015-08-26 12:46:27', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(113, 0, 44, 'JED Team Meeting Notes - 28 August 2015', 'jed-team-meeting-notes-28-august-2015', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">The Joomla! Extensions Directory Team (JED) Team meets the last Friday of every month at 6:00 AM PDT. This meeting was held on August 28th, 2015 on Glip.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Team Members</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #980000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Present:</span><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> Tessa Mero, Matthew Baylor, Luca Marzo, Jaz Parkyn</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #980000; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Absent:</span><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"> Ryan Bernstein, Claire Mandville, Keith Daudt, Amiel Horowitz, Anibal Sanchez, Mark Smeed, Markus Bopp, Mark Lee, Angelos Hadjiphillipou, Valentin Garcia, Renea Leathers, Paul Franklin, Hugh Douglas-Smith, Eyvonne Myers, Rodrigo Spillere</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Discussion Outline</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">The Joomla template was overhauled and needs to be implemented into the JED website. </span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Tessa Mero will follow up with current volunteer devs to see if they are still interested in working on the JED.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Matthew Baylor started working on a JED Contributor Agreement for people to sign before they can start as a Web Developer for the JED. About 20% done. Tasked every JED team member to review it within 7 days.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">When the Contributor Agreement is complete, it will need to be sent to the lawyer for approval.</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Include documentation for our end that covers how to update it whenever we have code changes, that way it&rsquo;s not tied to one person.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Start track all code contributors who accesses the code</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Set up a Vagrant box for community contributions.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: circle; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Have our developer volunteers give an explanation of what their plans are with the code and have them request approval first</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">By October 2015, the JED code will be ready</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">901 extension reviews were published in the last 28 days.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">188 tickets were processed in the last 28 days.</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">132 new extensions were approved in the last 28 days. 200 were submitted.</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Tickets: The &ldquo;New Listing Category&rdquo; has been completed. There are currently 17 pending tickets as of the last 4 days. We keep a promise of no later than 14 days. 4 days ago the queue was at 0. All pending/new tickets were complete.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Listings: There are currently 50 pending listings as of 10 days ago. We keep a promise of no later than 14 days. Tessa Mero tasked Listing Support members to have this complete. Luca and Jaz agreed to log in and clean up the queue.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Matthew Baylor suggests that JED code has such high confidentiality information, we need to up our screening method to bring in high quality volunteers without previous bad history with the JED if they are an extension developer.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Matthew Baylor and Tessa Mero suggests we have a reporting page on backend of JED to include very clear team reporting ability, such as how many tickets Tessa did this month. We are working on improving the sense of efficiency and also want to publically recognize contributions.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">3 potential volunteers are offering to help with support tickets. Tessa Mero completed training a new volunteer Monday August 24th, 2015 and will send an email for Matt to set up access.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">We discussed the importance of keeping communication open between team members when you aren&rsquo;t able to contribute for a period of time so we can find others to help.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.944; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.333333333333332px; font-family: Verdana; color: #4e4e4e; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Meeting ends after 80 minutes.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>', NULL, 1, 0, 0, 451, '2015-08-28 00:00:00', 451, '2015-08-28 14:16:58', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `#__volunteers_reports` (`id`, `department`, `team`, `title`, `alias`, `description`, `notes`, `state`, `ordering`, `version`, `created_by`, `created`, `modified_by`, `modified`, `checked_out`, `checked_out_time`) VALUES
	(114, 0, 52, 'Structural Team Meeting Minutes', 'structural-team-meeting-minutes', '<p>Present: Sarah, Ronni, Sander, Marijke</p>\r\n<p>Missing: Alice, Chris, Pete, George</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Out of the 10 nominees that where asked to confirm their interest in being part of the Transition Team 9 responded positively.</p>\r\n<p>The Stucture Team has prepared the required information and documentation for the vote in Leadership on which 6 members out of the 9 candidates that will be elected for the Transition Team.</p>\r\n<p>Once the Leadership Teams has elected the 6 Transition Team members from the community the 3 LT\'s will elect 1 member each for the Transition Team and the Team will begin its work to implement the new structures.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Timeplan:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The vote in Leadership will be started on the 1st of September and finished the 7th of September.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The results will be communicated directly to the Candidates hereafter and then the results will be made public on the 10th of September on the Leadership Blog.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>From the 10th of September to the 17th of September the 3 LT\'s (CLT, PLT &amp; OSM) will elect 1 member each to join the Transition Team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>On the 20th of September the final Transition Team members will be made public on the Leadership Blog.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Between the 20th of September and the 1st of October the Transition Team has an initial handover meeting with the Structure team.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>On the 1st of October the new Transition Team will officially take over from the Structure Team and implement the new structure.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Edit: Adjusted the candidate count.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>For reference here is a copy of the mail as it will be sent to the Leadership Teams private mailing list for the vote (all votes involving persons are on private mailing lists as well as information about all candidates due to consideration to people not elected):</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Transition Team Vote</span></p>\r\n<p><strong id="docs-internal-guid-4f02b109-8094-d7d9-9407-bbb9af6837eb" style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The call for the Transition Team nominees closed on July 31. We have received a total of 18 nominations, for 10 unique persons. 9 of them confirmed and accepted the nomination within the given deadline. </span></p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Voting details</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">This vote will be conducted using the same voting process that was used for the structure vote, with all three leadership teams voting. In order to have a valid vote on the candidates, at least 50% +1 (= 14) need to cast their votes on the candidates within the given time frame.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Please read carefully on how to vote, and follow the steps in best practices. If for some reason your votes shows an error, you will be contacted by the secretary. You will have only one chance to re-vote in that case, provided it can be done within the given timeframe.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Proxy</span></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">If for any reason you are not able to cast your vote in the given time frame, please consider to proxy your vote. The form includes a field where a proxy can be filled in.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14.6666666666667px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Voting Leadership members are:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">CLT: (6 voters)</span></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Guillermo Bravo</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Peter Bui</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14.666666666666666px; font-family: Arial; color: #00