round-repeat: initial;"><strong>UX Professional</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">We need people on board that are full time involved in UX. Remaining group members are to reach out.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;"><strong>Tasks</strong></p>\r\n<ul style="list-style-image: none; padding: 5px 40px; border: 1px dashed #bbbbbb; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 3px; color: #000000; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: normal; background: url(data:image/png;">\r\n<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">Expamding group. with full time professional UX peaple &nbsp;( Getting new UX professionals ) Cliff / Marco</li>\r\n<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">Handover from Crystal and Lucas ( David / Marco )</li>\r\n<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">Finalise minutest athens&nbsp;( David / Marco )</li>\r\n<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">Research / Persona\'s&nbsp;( tbd )</li>\r\n<li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">Backend UX / page builder ( tbd )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; background-image: url(\'data:image/png\'); background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 251px;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup><col style="width: 92pt;" width="123" /><col span="2" style="width: 48pt;" width="64" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 15pt;">