ial; background-repeat: initial;">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">## Welcome New Members</h3>\r\n<p><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;">Tito and Ryan are the two new members in the working group.</span><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /></p>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight: normal; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #000000; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0px !important; padding: 0px !important; background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">## Testing Code Sprint</h3>\r\n<p><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;">Dates for the 2015 Testing Code Sprint are 29, 30&nbsp;and 31 Oct. and 1st&nbsp;November. See:</span><a href="https://docs.joomla.org/Code_sprints" target="_blank" style="cursor: pointer; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; color: #1155cc !important; text-decoration: underline !important;">https://docs.joomla.org/Code_sprints&nbsp;<br /></a><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;">Anyone in the working&nbsp;group, who is interested in attending the code sprint and would like to participate needs to get in touch with Javier or Puneet.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;">Discussion about the current structure of the system Tests.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><br style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" /><span style="color: #000000; font-family: proxima-nova, \'Helvetica Neue\', HelvetitcaNeue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;">Javier and Puneet