	(329, 0, 13, '20 September 2016 - JUG Team Meeting Minutes', '20-september-2016-jug-team-meeting-minutes', '<p>In attendance:<br />Djamel Kherbi<br />Jenn Gress<br />Rowan Hoskyns-Abrahall</p>\r\n<p>Apologies:<br />Eric Lamy<br />Brian Ronnow</p>\r\n<p>No show:<br />Helvecio da Silva<br />Alejandro Pascoli<br />Bruce Balle</p>\r\n<p>The Events directory has been added to CJO! Yay! Hats off to Radek and Rowan for making this happen. One less subdomain! We do have an issue with a few JUGs that have the same listing owner for multiple JUGs. This needs to be resolved so that Events can display properly in conjunction with the JUG listings. Djamel will work with Kaduna and Petaling Jaya and Jenn will work with the Dutch JUGs.</p>\r\n<p>Jenn is going to JWC. Yay!</p>\r\n<p>Draft of email for JUG owners to review their listings will be sent out by September 27th.</p>\r\n<p>Djamel didn\'t hear back from Alejandro for training. He will follow up again.</p>\r\n<p>ACY Template is ready.</p>\r\n<p>Helpdesk issues are pretty well tamed. We may not replace it in the future.</p>\r\n<p>Djamel to lead the next meeting on 4 October 2016.</p>', NULL, 1, 16, 1, 535, '2016-09-20 17:43:51', 0, '2016-09-20 17:48:18', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
	(330, 0, 17, 'Certification Marketing Team - Meeting Notes september 20, 2016', 'certification-marketing-team-meeting-notes-septemb', '<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The Joomla! Certification Marketing Team (MT) meets every 2 weeks on monday at 20:00 PM CET. This meeting was held on September, 20th, 2016 on Glip, (this meeting was rescheduled to tuesday)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 16pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #434343; font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Team members</span></strong></h3>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">In attendance</span><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">: &nbsp;Richard van Tilborg, Andrea Gentil, Mike Veeckmans, Johan van der Velde.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Absents</span><span id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">: Elisa Foltyn, Robert Wilson, Sarah Watz, Rogelio Alvarado, Eric Lamy, Adamzy Lee, Andr&aacute;s R&aacute;tonyi.</span></span></p>\r\n<h3 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 16pt; margin-bottom: 4pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #434343; font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Discussion Outline</span></strong></h3>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">We start to make meeting notes for every meeting, after the meeting all the JCP MT members can review the document. After the review the meeting notes will be published on the Volunteers page and Facebook.</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height