he middle header need to be changed. (no black\\white image, use no badge in it. We gonna change this image. </span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">We gonna create the following groups into AcyMailing, then we can import the email addresses into the appropriate group:</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul style="margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;">\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: circle; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">JLP</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: circle; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">JUGS</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: circle; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">JoomlaDays</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: circle; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Voted people badge.</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Richard shared the information about his first official exam as JLP.</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The Landing page is reviewed by MWG.</span></strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir="ltr" style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: disc; background-color: transparent;">\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 2.3845; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong id="docs-internal-guid-6410b7e4-4907-9a9b-90de-dcb3f43ac14e" style="font-weight: normal;"><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Arial; font-size: 13.33px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Andrea and Richard are discussed the options to post news